Land of the Dead;;51;;74;;R;;In a world where zombies form the majority of the population, the remaining humans build a feudal society away from the undead. Ruthless Paul Kaufman (Dennis Hopper) rules and protects this microcosm but enforces painful class distinctions. Second-in-command Cholo DeMora (John Alberto Leguizamo) attempts to lead a secret rebellion against Kaufman's tyranny, but when the zombies begin to evolve, the survivors must discover a way to protect themselves from a zombie hoard that can learn and adapt.;;Horror;;George A. Romero;;2005;;Simon Baker,John Leguizamo,Asia Argento,Robert Joy,Dennis Hopper,Eugene Clark,Jennifer Baxter,Boyd Banks,Joanne Boland,Krista Bridges,Pedro Miguel Arce,Lara Amersey,Phil Fondacaro,Maxwell McCabe-Lokos,Sasha Roiz,Jonathan Walker;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/land_of_the_dead